Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Masaomi go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He went on ahead. He said he had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher the flames rise—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done, finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You only did what you thought was right, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:18.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the Dollars' leader, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the Dollars are behind this, then...we'll crush the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:06.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You go that way! Block off the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.09,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.67,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.23,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...to escape the shadow that was chasing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.49,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She just wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.20,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that brat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let her get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:44.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't feel anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:51.09,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The shock from what she had just seen was \Nthe only thing resonating throughout her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy that you're being released sooner than predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate what you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:31.43,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher incidents suddenly ceased after \Nthat night, and the city's peace was restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:36.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sonohara Anri's uneventful everyday \Nlife should have returned to her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got held up by class committee stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're going to start attending school again tomorrow, so you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll take your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado ran his heart out so he could hold those bags for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:08.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri, how much do you think I had to listen to this today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sonohara's getting discharged today!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will she be able to come to school tomorrow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anri's so erotically cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that last part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...thank you for coming to visit me so often, Kida and Ryugamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Masaomi, you just came out from the hospital, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've just missed her on my way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:36.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are my notes for the time you've been absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with using mine, I'll let you borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My handwriting's pretty bad, so they might be a bit hard to read, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's okay, feel free to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I brought this one today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.38,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida seems...somehow different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.89,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She felt vaguely discomforted by him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.01,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he first visited her in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There. That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What...happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:29.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's really nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, something just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to let Prince Mikado do the honors of escorting the princess back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get another chance like this for a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:58.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, an unknown feeling of insecurity enveloped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.77,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people have joined the Yellow Scarves recently, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.67,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:17.63,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They stand out much more than the \NDollars, since you can tell who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.14,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That gang had been around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.52,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like they've changed somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.26,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They've changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.23,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really put my finger on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:29.27,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're different from how they used to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.60,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like they've become more violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,140)}Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.03,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,260)}Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,380)}Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.03,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good evening, Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.02,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.50,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.37,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.54,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't familiar with the Internet before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.79,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,so you got a virus and that's how everything happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.20,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.43,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You're apologizing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Saika, do you know of a gang called the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.68,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the people who wear yellow cloth around the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.60,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.69,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also another group that's a lot like them called the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:19.16,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Slasher incidents, both of those groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...are in pretty dire straights right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.00,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.37,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest, Kanra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:32.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up that stuff with someone who doesn't know anything bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.97,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.54,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to know this stuff if you live in Ikebukuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:42.06,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrator in the Slasher case has yet to be caught, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:46.80,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, both the Yellow Scarves and the Dollars have had their members fall victim to the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:51.56,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they both think that the\N Slasher is in league with the other gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:57.74,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars don't seem so hung up on that idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:02.23,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know much about each other, \Nso I'm sure that breeds misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:11.62,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, if neither of them take matters into their own \Nhands with the Slasher, blood will rain down upon Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.15,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a real rivalry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.17,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything to worry about, Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.68,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Those gangs are running amuck of their own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:30.82,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the real perpetrator, so it \Ndoesn't matter if you come forward or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.57,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.48,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are really scary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.65,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They truly are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.16,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.40,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the traffic cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.41,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.61,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.79,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you about private conversations later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.76,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me, but this is it for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.87,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.84,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around, Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.88,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,'Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.39,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.10,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,290)}Saika has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.81,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I guess I'll be logging off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.72,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.73,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,130)}Setton has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.52,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Slasher incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.90,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know if I find anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,At a bargain price, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.29,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The real perpetrator has to be somewhere in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:30.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The sooner he's caught, the sooner the Yellow Scarves and the Dollars can clear up their misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll really be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:40.18,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the Yellow Scarves nor the \NDollars are completely cohesive groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:45.63,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be some people who shake down members of the other group in the name of that rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:58.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll simply turn into a real conflict if things keep going like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.86,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.74,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can stop it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:09.04,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing you can do about the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.70,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.53,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I'm looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.92,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to do something,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,thought the girl who houses an ethereal sword inside her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to do something,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.64,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,thought the girl who'd only seen the world through a picture frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:35.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...the boy who'd passed through that window and had visited her world was already restrained...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.07,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the heavy yoke of his own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He could no longer escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:05.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Something just came up with my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hate someone, hate my friend to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate doesn't cost anything, and it doesn't cause me any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect "two birds with one stone," it's "many wives for one man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Many wives for one man?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's really that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Kida's been acting strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it's not all in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:41.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:49.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that some of the Dollars \Nwere shaken down by the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were beaten to within an inch of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Scarves are the ones saying that the Slasher is part of the Dollars, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who leads the Dollars knew that things couldn't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:10.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he didn't yet know that he was \Nbeing used like a pawn on a chessboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Customers, eat sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi is the heart of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's true that he does a Cossack dance when you order take-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:25.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he was on a delivery when he followed those kids last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:31.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you swing that rod, I'm going to turn you into sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:35.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Human sushi... Ooh, it hurts and it tastes bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck sure doesn't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, those clouds look ominous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:58.24,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know anything about the Dollars or the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.04,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss is Kida Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him with you, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going to get revenge on your enemy, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.77,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, her children are unable to lie to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to a meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me to that meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.66,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...she found out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.04,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in the back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.38,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't run...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.35,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slash open those yellow children and love them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:03.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love them in your stead, since you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...want to hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.11,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy would find out that she's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She trembled in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:14.61,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.92,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And, standing there in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the female dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:44.23,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing the trapped girl could do was ask for help from someone like her who wasn't supposed to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It scaled the wall with her bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to make a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Are you serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here. Hop on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that suit seems a little tight for a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:47.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a guy, but I could \Nlove you just for the suit if you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They do say, "love the Buddha, love his clothes."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.46,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guy who's always with Mikado and Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want him to see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.94,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the situation, but I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.06,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew one of them had to be the legendary headless horseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The fragments of information they knew came together in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruder wielded a sword like that of the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.83,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And the black biker had come to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There were also rumors that the black biker was part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.08,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They all arrived at the same conclusion:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the Slasher is part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:17.58,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy didn't know whether or not that conclusion was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But what he did know was that no \Nmatter how much he thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.60,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't be able to restrain \Nthose who had witnessed this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about dullahans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Umm... No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They visit the homes of those who're about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're headless knights who ride headless horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess they're like the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.58,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy suddenly thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.87,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone amongst us may die..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...do I want to see Saki at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.60,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"The blue dynasty is dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"The sky has fallen."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:07.42,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the slogan that a certain yellow flag-toting group used in the Annals of the Three Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly isn't very blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not very yellow, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:16.69,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,200)}Tanaka Taro has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.20,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,330)}Tanaka Taro has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.94,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,450)}Tanaka Taro has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,195)}Kanra has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,325)}Kanra has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,450)}Kanra has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.94,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Gooood evenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.03,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the only one here, Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:21.73,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.98,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.44,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting right off with a private conversation, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.86,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:32.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have the Yellow Scarves always been in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They started up about three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.73,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, they were fairly docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:46.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who leads the Dollars learned about the heated \Nrivalry between the Blue Squares and the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:51.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He remained unaware of the fact that his best friend's former girlfriend was a casualty of that conflict...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:56.39,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that the man who was answering his \Nquestions controlled the mind of that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:59.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as left an incurable wound on his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.45,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...So, only the Yellow Scarves survived—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.44,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Blue Squares didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Yellow Scarves got tired of fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.99,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,and after he left,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:16.25,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,they joined the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean they merged?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:28.21,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure neither gang—outside of their respective leaders—\Ncared enough to find out where people came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.80,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,After they threw off their blue uniforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:34.97,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd get the OK just for saying,\N "I want to be in the Yellow Scarves."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.20,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the leader who quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.01,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:45.57,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the guys who sent his girlfriend to the \Nhospital are now hanging with his old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:52.81,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there are some guys who are in \Nboth the Dollars and the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:20:00.79,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I spread the word that we had no part in this, \Nthen they'll be likely to pass it on to the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,If it truly isn't the work of the Dollars, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:10.89,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars don't have any rules, and it's not like you control everyone's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,While you weren't looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.47,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...some member of the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.65,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...could have become the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.79,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's the Dollars' system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're planning to come over to this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.36,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.15,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You don't sound too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you haven't fully recovered...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, 'morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:59.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I just met Kida at the station and he said he's not coming to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:01.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. He didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:04.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run from the past, Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worrying about something to do with that past, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't run from it, then you should just face it head on and beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could settle everything with your past too, just by fighting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could fight you, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.30,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He simply wanted a place where he belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time he talked with his childhood friend about his new home,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:45.07,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd feel uneasy about his existence, which \Nwas draped in hand-me-downs from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.27,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He now understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:51.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...that amongst the Yellow Scarves, the place where he belonged...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:56.41,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...was with a single person named Mikajima Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:22:03.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, his motivation springs from having found a new place with an important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's raining again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadota...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:25.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, so I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:02.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some great person once said, "The world is a construct of the mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some great person once said, "The world is a symbol."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detestable past is the product of your imagination.
